		<p>FireFox, <a href="http://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/Cookies">http://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/Cookies</a></p>
		<p>Internet Explorer, <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/info/cookies.mspx">https://www.microsoft.com/info/cookies.mspx</a></p>
